1e:["$","p",null,{"children":["Now we need to jump into the CSS. SVG provides us with two properties called ",["$","code",null,{"children":"stroke-dasharray"}]," and ",["$","code",null,{"children":"stroke-dashoffset"}]," that we can use to add a dashed effect to our circle. Setting both properties to 100 will give us the following:"]}]
