25:["$","p",null,{"children":"Now that the effect has been demonstrated, it's now a case of working out how a given percentage maps to the stroke-dashoffset value. Quick warning, this requires a basic understanding of maths!"}]
26:["$","p",null,{"children":"Here we're going to do this in Sass, however it's certainly possible to do this on the client in JavaScript and the CSSOM (although watch out for floating points)."}]
